profile:
Shop RHW is a Toronto-based studio with a focus on solid wood custom furniture hand crafted by Rundell Haynes-Wells. 
In addition to being a craftsman, he also offers custom design consultation and renderings.

Rundell combines years of experience problem solving, exploring, and innovating, and has been a maker of things all of his life. 
He’s a natural born collaborator and is generous with the information he shares with his clients in the hope that more knowledge and understanding of custom furniture will inspire sustained interest and appreciation.

Please give me a call - 647-453-0093

profile:
Professional, precise, perfect installation every time. Your satisfaction and peace of mind is our only goal.

We know your time is valuable so we always strive to be sensitive to the constraints of your busy schedule. Same day service is generally very doable, as well as evenings and weekends. 

We aim to offer the most premier design, installation and assembly services in the Toronto, GTA and surrounding areas. We work closely with all our clients to make sure every project is completed to our exacting standards. We will not rest until you are fully satisfied and thrilled with the final results.

So whether you need a kitchen designed and installed or house full of furniture put together or an organization solution figured out we have you covered. Or maybe you want to know what would be the best types of curtains or blinds to put in your house or condo? Let us advise you. If you want to make the most efficient use of your space we know what furniture makes the most sense. These services and more are what we wish to facilitate for you…

We can handle any project – large or small. Give us a call, text or email and we will be happy to resolve any questions you may have!

With our 25 years of combined installation experience and knowledge you can rest assured that your job will be done to the highest standards in our industry.
